---
title: Smart Pork Chops and Apricot Sauce with Thyme Roasted Veggie Medley
description: Pork chops love to cozy up with something sweet, and what could be sweeter than a smooth apricot-mustard sauce? To go alongside, a medley of veggies get roasted in a sprinkling of  thyme for extra oomph!

